{"id":"23031","name":"我將，巡徵追獵","rarity":5,"path":"Rogue","desc":"「可悲可笑的奴隸們……」\n浩蕩的豐饒民軍隊壓境而來，狼毒如洪水般湧向青丘軍，試圖喚起軍士深埋於心中的恐懼，化作種種恐怖的幻象，使他們垂下武器，猶豫不前。\n但陣線猶如銅牆鐵壁，不為步離人輕蔑的話音所動，一個身影緩步走出。\n她緩緩活動著身體，無形的煞氣衝擊下，旗幟獵獵作響。\n「將軍，是將軍出現了……」\n「飛霄將軍……」\n「『天擊』將軍！」\n細微的呼喚匯聚起來，化作震天的戰吼。\n「翾翔不墜，萬載常勝！」\n她站在那裡。一個人，就像一支軍隊。","icon":"icon/light_cone/23031.png","preview":"image/light_cone_preview/23031.png","portrait":"image/light_cone_portrait/23031.png","ranks":{"id":"23031","skill":"震懾","desc":"使裝備者的暴擊率提高#1[f1]%。裝備者發動追加攻擊時，獲得1層【流光】，最多疊加#3[i]層。每層【流光】使裝備者造成的終結技傷害無視目標#2[i]%的防禦力。裝備者回合結束時，移除1層【流光】。","params":[[0.15,0.27,2],[0.175,0.3,2],[0.2,0.33,2],[0.225,0.36,2],[0.25,0.39,2]],"properties":[[{"type":"CriticalChanceBase","value":0.15}],[{"type":"CriticalChanceBase","value":0.175}],[{"type":"CriticalChanceBase","value":0.2}],[{"type":"CriticalChanceBase","value":0.225}],[{"type":"CriticalChanceBase","value":0.25}]]},"promotions":{"id":"23031","values":[{"hp":{"base":43.2,"step":6.48},"atk":{"base":28.8,"step":4.32},"def":{"base":21,"step":3.15}},{"hp":{"base":95.04,"step":6.48},"atk":{"base":63.36,"step":4.32},"def":{"base":46.2,"step":3.15}},{"hp":{"base":164.16,"step":6.48},"atk":{"base":109.44,"step":4.32},"def":{"base":79.8,"step":3.15}},{"hp":{"base":233.28,"step":6.48},"atk":{"base":155.52,"step":4.32},"def":{"base":113.4,"step":3.15}},{"hp":{"base":302.4,"step":6.48},"atk":{"base":201.6,"step":4.32},"def":{"base":147,"step":3.15}},{"hp":{"base":371.52,"step":6.48},"atk":{"base":247.68,"step":4.32},"def":{"base":180.6,"step":3.15}},{"hp":{"base":440.64,"step":6.48},"atk":{"base":293.76,"step":4.32},"def":{"base":214.2,"step":3.15}}],"materials":[[{"id":"2","num":5000},{"id":"113011","num":8}],[{"id":"2","num":10000},{"id":"110191","num":4},{"id":"113011","num":12}],[{"id":"2","num":20000},{"id":"110192","num":4},{"id":"113012","num":8}],[{"id":"2","num":50000},{"id":"110192","num":8},{"id":"113012","num":12}],[{"id":"2","num":100000},{"id":"110193","num":5},{"id":"113013","num":6}],[{"id":"2","nu